China Seeks End of Coal Trade Curbs, China Coal Resource Says

-- B y   A l i s t a i r   H o l l o w a y
-- 
2011-06-16T10:03:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-16/china-seeks-end-of-coal-trade-curbs-china-coal-resource-says.html
China’s National Development and
Reform Commission asked the country’s main coal producing
regions to end restrictions on deliveries to other provinces,
 China Coal Resource  reported yesterday, citing a government
official it did not name.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alistair Holloway in London at 
 aholloway1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net . 